Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到在这镇上会遇到布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然想尽方法要跟你取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管看到你身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚在这镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我自己也在这里生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的居所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为这样 就让我满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道保护重要的人是多么困难的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是单纯的满足着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好气派的迟到啊 布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会"不是"吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样沉默寡言又幼稚的家伙居然也有对象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢在我之前成家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非杀了你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也介绍女人给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止 加利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百五十三号的客人没有还钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠地给他点颜色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登 待会再慢慢听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不要去刚才见面的女孩的学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚上头的人是这么命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登 你到底干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 千万别忘了这条命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在最底层 你也是组织的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头的命令是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惟有服从这一条才能在组织里待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会打架还想混饭吃的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Millennion里是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的老大Big Daddy创造了Millennion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括了它的真谛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 遇见玛丽亚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我就想会这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还被组织给警告了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 她住在Big Daddy的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味着能和组织上头接触
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一一个不慎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会让想干掉Big Daddy的敌对组织知道玛丽亚的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会给Daddy带来危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要防患于未然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我早就了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还是想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换到我的立场上想想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布兰登·西特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请你等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢垂钓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂钓 就是钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…一次也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:08:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就这样 让诱饵像活的一样去引鱼儿上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的资质不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有一个可称得上挚友的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是十五年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人犯了罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了补偿所犯的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他收养了一个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他决定即使舍弃自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要抚养这位少女成人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使她不再生活在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一个充满阳光的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但挚友的愿望还没达成就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我决定为了完成他的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续收养那位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 布兰登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见她的话 到我的别墅来也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要再在其他地方再和她见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽全组织的力量来保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把你的鱼竿提起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 只顾用力的话线会断的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着它挣扎的方向来用力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daddy在这个城市 还只是沙漠和稀落的草地时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就移民过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候比现在还要混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们纷争不息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy为了保护邻居和朋友而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无关是与非 只为了生存下去而战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后随着镇子的扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy要保护的也越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护数十上百有如家人般的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy创建了组织 Millennion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 只是为了守护而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续迟到的道歉就用这东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有男人在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么处理这东西啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就交给我老妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚到我家来吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大秘藏的波旁酒也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没想到布兰登还有这种兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是不爱讲话 但有了鱼就不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 我是执事时冈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大的房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最初也完全不习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登 你现在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没干危险的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作 送货的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道哈利也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你们都好好在工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 就我一个住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 学校毕业以后进公司工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想一个人生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠自己的力量来生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是说要离开这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才…叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 要是连玛丽亚都失去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你一直呆在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍 我的朋友布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫布兰登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登吗 今后玛丽亚就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来我成电灯泡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我烤了派 想三个人一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要取消宴会？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 兰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"闪电"那边的人好像开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从某方面得到的情报看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在打今晚宴会的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次的宴会是Big Daddy的商界人士招待会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在中止的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以防万一还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会照原定计划举行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只要去收集"闪电"的情报就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就交给我和我的部下来办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交给你了 贝尔·沃肯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利 鲍勃送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先下手的好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管花多少钱都不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去收集"闪电"的情报去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样能参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服很适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个头发有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们去跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 我们公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑以后以Millennion的事业为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你们建立更加密切的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标只是Millennion老大的人头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要误伤其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领路的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行得很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有一个人潜入进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挡道了 快滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 "闪电"的诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Millennion！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是"闪电"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前见过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我一次很好的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Millennion的哈利·麦克道韦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打听到了"闪电"要来袭击的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就擅自行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想往上爬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我先记下你们干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧回你们的老巢去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦屁股这种事就交给我们干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们公司也会诚心诚意地尽全力做好这个项目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也不会辜负您的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住 布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个少年是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰迪 快叫救护车来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 把您留在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 请您一定要小心 Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊 布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么要保护我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了组织吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是为了玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰登
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么举枪 为什么开枪 为什么杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐停滞的意识中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是浮现出了玛丽亚和哈利的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我一直在思考"守护"的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.14,0:24:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人默默地扣动了扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火光又夺去了一个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Millennion的布兰登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为Sweeper的男人
